headline: New Garmin OnBoard System redefines boating safety tech
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN), the world's largest1 and most innovative marine electronics manufacturer, today announced Garmin OnBoard™, a versatile Man Overboard (MOB) and engine cutoff solution for boaters that uses wireless technology instead of traditional tethered cords.
